### 3. Progress Bars

**When to use:**
- Operations >10 seconds
- File uploads/downloads
- Multi-step processes
- Any duration-determinable task

**Specifications:**
```css
/* Linear progress bar */
.progress-bar {
  width: 100%;
  height: 8px;
  background: #E5E7EB;
  border-radius: 4px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.progress-fill {
  height: 100%;
  background: #3B82F6;
