#### Aggregation Pipeline
```javascript
// Complex aggregation example
db.orders.aggregate([
  // Stage 1: Match recent orders
  {
    $match: {
      created_at: { $gte: new Date("2024-01-01") },
      status: "completed"
    }
  },

  // Stage 2: Lookup user data
